storyInfo: See new sights, meet new people. The sights that Asbestos sees, see her too.

attributes.content: Here. Gavial told me you're with Rhodes Island too.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: My lieutenants are all businessmen. I've taught them a little Sargonian. Talk to them if you need anything.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Alright. But why's that one staring at me?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: We don't get many guests here, so it's a bit of an occasion.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: It is for me, at least!
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Look at that tail!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Long and fleshy... It looks so soft and flexible too... Are those orange patterns on it?
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Look, she's carrying all that stuff with her tail! And lifting that heavy door with one hand! Wow!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: She must be really good at wrestling. That tail looks like it could break a tree in half. She's so beautiful!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: I've never seen someone like that. I wanna be friends with her!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Wait, you're going up to her just like that? I, I'm not sure... whoa...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Metal Crab armor, Metal Crab greaves! Their hard shells stop any attack!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Sawfin tooth hammer and Sawfin bone sword! Their sharp edges cut through anything!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: (She's coming...!)
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Hey, hello!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Something wrong?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh! Well, I like your tail!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: My tail? The hell are you talking about?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: I'm busy. Outta my way!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: (Whoa! She's scary...)
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Oh, wait!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: No need to be angry, right? I said I like you!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: What about you? Don't you think my tail's nice? People say I've got a cool tail!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Ha? What're you on about now?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Go play in the mud with your friend.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: You speak our language? In a pretty rowdy way, though...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: I'm not playing in the mud! Did you think I'm a kid or something?
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: ...We'll have a fight!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Seriously, what's wrong with you?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Outta my way!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Are you nuts?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Fine, you're nice, your tail's nice, super nice!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh? C'mon, gimme a break!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: It's a fight!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Hey, watch out—woo, that's right, get your tail round her neck!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Oh no, my oil—hey, that was neat, using oil to slip out!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Woo! Fight! Fight!
attributes.name: Group of Archosauria

attributes.content: Quick, this bush will hide us.
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Haven't you guys fought enough yesterday? Why do I have to be here too?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: And what about you two?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: She bought a bunch of stuff. Of course we want to check it out.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: She took a few scales off my tail last time!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: She bought all that stuff, but she's living in a shed out here instead of in the village?
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Not a bad spot though. That tree isn't too far from the river, but not so close that it would get flooded.
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: S-She caught a huge bug!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: She's frying it!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: She's putting it on bread!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: She ate it!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Ughh...
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Look at her, she's putting rocks in her soup.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: That's the kind of salty rock that gives it more flavor. How did she know about them? I don't think anyone in the village told her.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Hey, she knows about those vines that you told me about too. The ones that have a tangy sweetness when you chew them.
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Is she going out to catch fins?
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Maybe striped fins, but sawfins aren't so easy to catch. I've caught a few with my tail, but it hurts quite a bit.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Maybe outsiders can learn about the rocks and vines, but when it comes to fins—
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Ha!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: How did she do that?
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Pff.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Let's go and find some vines.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Two hours later
Um, uh...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Still tailing me? Did you think I didn't see you?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: What about your friend? Eaten by fins?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Er, no, she saw you eat the bugs and got hungry too, but—
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Looks like she ate the wrong kind!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: C-Can you help us out?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Eh?!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: What is WRONG with you people?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: It was because you ate them...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: So what kind did she eat? How many?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Not sure... and just a few.
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Did she vomit? Is she conscious? Are there any spots on her skin? Swelling?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Er...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Forget it, I'll take a look myself.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: No fever, no rashes. Take this herb and boil it in water. It'll make her throw up.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Give her plenty of water.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: She threw up three times until there was nothing left, then fell asleep.
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Is she gonna be okay?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Just give her more water and stop yapping already!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: The fire is so warm.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: I want to sing.
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Heh, me too!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: We love a muscle that's big and whole~♪
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: You farm, and I hunt~ There's teeth white and tough in my little runts~♪
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Hey!♪
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Seriously, why are you people still here? What am I, your mom?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Are you saying you're our mother? What do you mean?
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Maybe it's the tail? She's got a tail too. Maybe we're relatives!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Where are you from, Mom?
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: W-Why do you eat bugs, Mom?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: And why come here? You bought my stuff too. Are you gonna live here?
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Just— *Sigh*... I...
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: I'm not your mom, and I'm here to climb the waterfall.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: You've gotta be kidding, no one's ever climbed it!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Yeah, yeah, whatever.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Then why are you climbing it? You'll die! And what for? Are there more fins up there?
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: ...For the view.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: The view? From the waterfall? Can't you find those anywhere?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: It's exciting. Climbing it'll be fun.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: What? How is that exciting? We're happy enough just living here and getting our three meals a day.
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Yeah, this is where we live. Plus, what if there's a bunch of poisonous bugs up there? You'll die! That's not exciting.
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Yeah, you'll die! Don't be silly!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: We saw you eat bugs. Did you spend all your money shopping a few days ago? But you can make money if you catch a bunch of fins!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Yeah, follow Inam and you'll make lots of money!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: And your parents will be sad if you die!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Parents? They ain't around anymore.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh.
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: But what's with all this death talk? Never said I was gonna die.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh, that's good.
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Then let's keep singing! Do you want to learn our songs?
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: You farm—♪
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh for god's sake stop talking already even that girl wasn't as noisy as you people I should've gotten some duct tape to shut you up for good!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Whoa! What did she say? That wasn't Sargonian, was it?
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Did one of her eyes just change color?
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Argh! Ugh! Uhhhh...
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Finally! She's awake! Now you can take her and scram!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Are you alright?
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Ugh... guh...
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Shit, and out like a light again.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Whatever. You have doctors, don't you? Stop wasting time with me.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Now piss off.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Alright, thank you, miss!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: (Doesn't change the fact that she's weird through. Maybe we should knock her out and take her away in a sack if things don't go well.)
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Hell no!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Oh, it's morning.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Yesterday was so tiring... I should go before those guys come back.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Looks like that's everything. Time to move!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: And here we are.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: It's even more daunting up close. What am I getting myself into?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Well, here goes nothing!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: The surroundings are silent, save for the deafening roar of the waterfall. Asbestos climbs against the raging current, tugging at her rope, the top of which is swallowed by the splashing foam.
It is always the same—climbing towards unknown heights, or descending into unknown depths.
She knows that there is a stunning view at her destination, but not what difficulties that she might encounter on the way.
It could be a slip, a fall, wild beasts, snowstorms, or perhaps some disaster or challenge she could never imagine.
(The current's too strong. I can't find my footing!)
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: (There's a branch there!)
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: (Good, it's pretty solid. I should be able to avoid the currents by following it...)
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Ha!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: So slippery!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: She knows how it feels to lose her balance in rapid currents, pushing her lungs to the limit in suffocating whirlpools.
She knows how it feels to keep climbing through the night after breaking her arm from a fall halfway up, just to catch a glimpse of the sunrise from the top.
She knows how it feels to slip and fall on a glacier, the ice chips ripping through her skin.
But she also remembers seeing the rays of the setting sun reflect upon the icy surface when she stood up again, accompanied by a sweet icy breeze.
At that moment, Asbestos no longer cared about her bleeding wounds. All the pain and suffering, all the hardship—it was all worth it.
*Cough* *Cough*...
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Aye, that was one hell of a shower... good thing there's a gap here.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: But I'm still alive! And almost there!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Here we go!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Every time she gets up again, she is thinking the same thing.
It was bloody worth it.
Half an hour later
*gasp*... *gasp*...
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: I'm exhausted...
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: I took a look around. No poisonous bugs, so she won't die. Oh, and these vines grow here too? Wow, there's a lot of them!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: It's such a great place up here! So many vines growing here!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Haha, you may be fierce, but you're pretty darn good!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Hey, back off!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: I had my eyes on her first!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Oh, and sorry about the other day. Kanna told me you outsiders don't like fighting. I shouldn't have hit you.
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: But your tail is really cool!
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Oh, for the love of—!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Just shut up and take in the view!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: The Archosauria are wet and muddy, with pieces of grass in their hair.
A wind from the canyon blows the grass into the sky, until it disappears in the distance.
They see a sight they have never seen before—their own home.
Look over there!
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: Wow! Look at that!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Their hearts are filled with myriad emotions. Beautiful, stunning, spectacular—or perhaps something beyond what any word could describe. Just like the outsider who gazes at the view in fascination, their cries of joy echo through the canyon.
Woo!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Wahoo!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Wow...
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: It's beautiful.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Wow...
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: I want to sing.
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Let's surround her! Join hands and sing!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Your waterfall is rushing, there's fins for your plate~♪
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: You swing about your tail, so the fins take the bait~♪
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Climb up your waterfall, it's such a pretty sight~♪
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: It's such a pretty sight, oh, such a pretty sight~♪
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Ha. Fine.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Such a pretty sight~♪
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Hey, stop spinning!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Cheer and laugh, till we make the sky sing~♪
attributes.name: Frank Archosauria

attributes.content: Make the sky sing~♪
attributes.name: Shy Archosauria

attributes.content: We'll be going!
attributes.name: Happy Archosauria

attributes.content: Goodbye, friend!
attributes.name: Serious Archosauria

attributes.content: Yeah, yeah, later guys!
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: So tired.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Where do they get the energy for all that noise? I'd rather climb ten waterfalls.
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: Now, what should I write for this one?
attributes.name: Asbestos

attributes.content: One month later
Magazine delivery from Asbestos! There's one for everyone! Her travel journal's inside.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: A travel journal is a record you keep of what you see and experience when you visit a new place.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Wow, she grades the sights pretty harshly. And she looked so happy when she came down from the waterfall.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: It's in Rim Billitonian. I'll translate it. There's a new section: 'Meet the Locals.' You guys are in it!
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: We're in a book!
attributes.name: Group of Archosauria

attributes.content: Ahem! It opens like this:
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: 'They're noisy, but fun.'
attributes.name: Asbestos
